## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The data is primarily from Western contexts, which may not fully represent global educational inequalities. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources means that some nuances of the original research may not be fully captured. Further empirical research is needed to explore the complexities of social class and education in diverse settings.

